  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nThis is some logs from Nimbus test\r\n[lodestarFull.log](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/11870761/lodestarFull.log)\r\n\r\nit shows that Lodestar calls `network.unsubscribeGossipCoreTopics()` multiple times while it's only supposed to call 1 time and then the control flag would toggle\r\n\r\n```\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.033[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.035[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.035[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.049[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.049[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.050[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.050[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.051[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.051[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.055[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.056[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.060[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.061[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.082[sync]             \u001B[33mwarn\u001B[39m: Node sync has fallen behind by 81 slots\r\nJun-23 23:28:12.083[sync]             \u001B[32minfo\u001B[39m: Un-subscribed gossip core topics\r\n```\r\n\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThis log should be printed once: `Un-subscribed gossip core topics`\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nNimbus tested to restarted some EL and CL multiple times\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nv1.9.0",
